description:
The Converse All Star Chuck '70 is a renewed sneaker with modern details that pay tribute to the original Chuck Taylor All Star from the 70s. It has a slightly higher rubber sole edge, a cushioning footbed for long-lasting comfort and a somewhat larger rubber toe cap. Other vintage details include stitching on the side and a thicker canvas upper for more comfort and sturdiness. And of course, the classic Chuck Taylor features such as the star on the ankle and the outsole of vulcanized rubber are not missing.
